enro hold buy enro shirt and foxcroft enro hold corp said it acquir enro shirt co and foxcroft ltd from wilson bro for 30 mln dlr . enro hold is own 50 pct by investor and 50 pct by manag and other . the investor group bought 50 pct of the common equiti and suppli five mln dlr in mezzanin financ . manag bought the other 50 pct . congress financ group suppli 28 mln dlr in senior financ and the seller took back a note for 12.1 mln dlr . enro shirt ha annual sale of about 42 mln dlr and foxcroft ha sale of about 13 mln dlr .